tags.description: Prophesy Wall, located near St. George, Utah, a sandstone multi-pitch sport area offering over 50 bolted multi-pitch routes ranging from 5.7 to 5.12a grades. The wall features solid, juggy holds and varnished edges, with climbs up to 250 feet in length.
tags.name: Prophesy Wall
West Canyon Cliff
tags.note: Annual climbing closure February 1 - June 1 to protect nesting sites
